snippet.title: Funny CATS DESTROYING EVERYTHING on their way! - PREPARE to LAUGH SUPER HARD!
snippet.description:
Cats are the best animals ever, they are so cute and they make us laugh all the time! But sometimes they can be also annoying because they break everything on their way! Just look how all these cats and kittens destroy curtains, toilet paper, glasses, windows, plates, flowers,... So ridiculous and funny!  What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
